Introduction

Son Na Eun (손나은) is a South Korean singer and Actress. She is best known for being the Visual and Center of the Korean pop girl group APink. Aside from being one of the it girls of Kpop, Naeun has starred in numerous Music Videos, Movies, and even Dramas.

She mader her debut as a member of Apink on April 21, 2011.

In April 2021, Naeun left IST Entertainment although she remains as a member of Apink. Soon after, she joined YG Entertainment as an actress.

In April 2022, Naeun announced that she will leave Apink after 11 years.
